Package: htcrosstabs
Type: Package
Title: Generate simple crosstabs (HealthTree Foundation)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    "Alex", "Brown",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "alexb@healthtree.org",
    comment = NULL
  )
Description: Creating crosstabs in the way that HealthTree Foundation likes
    them. Built to handle numeric data, likert-like data, and categorical data
    (including multi-answer). Contains pre-built tables as well as functions
    for easily adding lines yourself.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
